---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About -- 24K Labs" description="24K Labs builds AI code services on the x402 protocol. Founded in Philadelphia, 2026.">

  <section class="page-header">
    <div class="page-header__glow"></div>
    <div class="container">
      <span class="page-header__badge">About</span>
      <h1 class="page-header__title">24K Labs</h1>
      <p class="page-header__desc">
        AI services that work the way the internet was supposed to work.
        Request, pay, done.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose reveal">
        <h2>Who We Are</h2>
        <p>
          24K Labs is a small, independent company founded in 2026 in Philadelphia.
          We build AI-powered code analysis services and sell them through the
          x402 protocol -- no subscriptions, no API keys, no middlemen.
        </p>
        <p>
          We're not trying to be a platform. We're building useful tools and selling them
          the simplest way possible: you send a request, you pay for it, you get your result.
          That's it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-surface);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose reveal">
        <h2>The Mission</h2>
        <p>
          Make AI services accessible through open payment protocols.
        </p>
        <p>
          The current model for selling AI services is broken. You sign up for an account,
          get an API key, connect a credit card, manage billing, rotate secrets, and hope
          the provider doesn't change their pricing. It's a lot of overhead for what should
          be a simple transaction.
        </p>
        <p>
          x402 fixes this. It turns every HTTP endpoint into a self-describing,
          self-pricing service. Any client -- human or AI agent -- can discover what's available,
          see the price, pay, and get the result. No accounts. No dashboards. No billing surprises.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="prose reveal">
        <h2>The x402 Vision</h2>
        <p>
          We're building toward a world where AI agents are first-class economic actors.
          An agent with a USDC balance should be able to browse the web, discover services,
          compare prices, and pay for what it needs -- all without a human managing credentials
          or approving invoices.
        </p>
        <p>
          That world needs open infrastructure, not walled gardens. x402 is that infrastructure,
          and we're proud to be one of the first companies building real services on top of it.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section" style="background: var(--bg-surface);">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="grid-2 reveal">
        <div>
          <h2 class="value__title">Open Source</h2>
          <p class="value__desc">
            We build in public. Our tools, our research, and our learnings go back to the community.
            The x402 ecosystem grows faster when everyone can see how things work.
          </p>
          <a href="https://github.com/Haustorium12" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--outline" style="margin-top: 16px;">
            GitHub &#8599;
          </a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <h2 class="value__title">Built in Philly</h2>
          <p class="value__desc">
            Philadelphia, PA. Not Silicon Valley, not a coworking space in Lisbon.
            A real city with real problems and a long history of people figuring things out.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="coming-soon reveal">
        <h2 class="coming-soon__title">Get in Touch</h2>
        <p class="coming-soon__desc">
          Questions, partnerships, or just want to talk about x402 --
          find us on GitHub or try the demo.
        </p>
        <div style="margin-top: 24px; display: flex; gap: 12px; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;">
          <a href="https://github.com/Haustorium12" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="btn btn--primary">
            GitHub &#8599;
          </a>
          <a href="/#demo" class="btn btn--outline">Try the Demo</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .value__title {
    font-size: 1.4rem;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .value__desc {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }
</style>
